velho Michael Scott.

387
00:20:01,034 --> 00:20:02,785
Novo e melhorado.

388
00:20:03,745 --> 00:20:05,038
Querem saber?

389
00:20:05,288 --> 00:20:06,706
Amo a Phyllis.

390
00:20:08,583 --> 00:20:10,084
